{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>acceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>accelerationIncludingGravity</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/interval\"><code>interval</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/rotationRate\"><code>rotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Device Orientation Events に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventAcceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEventAcceleration</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventRotationRate\"><code>DeviceMotionEventRotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceOrientationEvent\"><code>DeviceOrientationEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"サマリー","title":"サマリー","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code> はウェブ開発者にデバイスの位置と向きの変更スピードの情報を提供します。</p>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>警告:</strong> 現在、Firefox と Chrome は同じ方法で座標を処理しません。これらを使用する際は、注意してください。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"コンストラクター","title":"コンストラクター","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.devicemotionevent_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.DeviceMotionEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>新しい <code>DeviceMotionEvent</code> を生成します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"プロパティ","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.acceleration_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>3 つの軸 X、Y、Z 上のデバイスの加速度を与えるオブジェクトです。加速度は <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">m/s<sup>2</sup></a> で表されます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.accelerationincludinggravity_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>X、Y、Z 上のデバイスの加速度を重力度込みで与えるオブジェクトです。加速度は <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">m/s<sup>2</sup></a> で表されます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.rotationrate_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/rotationRate\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.rotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>3つの方向軸アルファ、ベータ、ガンマ上のデバイスの向きの変化率を与えるオブジェクトです。回転速度は 1 秒あたりの度数で表されます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.interval_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/interval\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.interval</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>デバイスからデータを取得する間隔（ミリ秒）を表す数値です。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'devicemotion'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>acceleration<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">' m/s2'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">ステータス</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/deviceorientation/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"DeviceOrientation Event Specificationの仕様書\" rel=\" noopener\">DeviceOrientation Event Specification</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-ed\">編集者草案</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザー実装状況","id":"ブラウザー実装状況","isH3":false,"query":"api.DeviceMotionEvent","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連項目","title":"関連項目","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/deviceorientation_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">deviceorientation (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></a></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/devicemotion_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">devicemotion (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Events/Detecting_device_orientation\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">デバイスの方向検出 (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Events/Orientation_and_motion_data_explained\" title=\"向きと動作データの説明\">向きと動作データの説明</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"サマリー","id":"サマリー"},{"text":"コンストラクター","id":"コンストラクター"},{"text":"プロパティ","id":"プロパティ"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様","id":"仕様"},{"text":"ブラウザー実装状況","id":"ブラウザー実装状況"},{"text":"関連項目","id":"関連項目"}],"summary":"DeviceMotionEvent はウェブ開発者にデバイスの位置と向きの変更スピードの情報を提供します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/devicemotionevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/devicemotionevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent","title":"DeviceMotionEvent"}],"pageTitle":"DeviceMotionEvent - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}